author: The Critical Drinker
description: Its been ten years in the making, but the final season of Stranger Things is here at last. Well, the first part of the final season because for some reason we're splitting it up into volumes for this thing. Anyway, was it worth the wait? Will it be the last ever piece of event TV? Join me for my review.
title: Stranger Things Season 5 - The Last Real TV Event?
